==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exigenter
<hw>Ex"i*gent*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(O. Eng.
Law)</fld> <def>An officer in the Court of King's Bench and Common Pleas
whose duty it was to make out exigents. The office is now
abolished.</def> <rj><au>Cowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exigible</ent>⟦br⟧
